de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.tnccs.session.statemachine.simple

Class DefaultClientServerWorkingState

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.tnccs.session.statemachine.AbstractState

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ServerWorking, State

     class DefaultClientServerWorkingState
extends AbstractState
implements ServerWorking
    Default TNCC server working state. The TNCC listens for further messages in the server working state and changes the state according to a newly received message.
